General Assembly Raised Bill No. 5160
February Session, 2026 LCO No. 855
Referred to Committee on HOUSING
Introduced by:
(HSG)
AN ACT APPROPRIATING FUNDS TO ASSIST HOMELESS
PERSONS.
Be it enacted by the Senate and House of Representatives in General
Assembly convened:
1 Section 1. (Effective July 1, 2026) The sum of thirty-three million five
2 hundred thousand dollars is appropriated to the Department of
3 Housing from the General Fund, for the fiscal year ending June 30, 2027,
4 for programs to assist homeless persons.
This act shall take effect as follows and shall amend the following
sections:
Section 1 July 1, 2026 New section
Statement of Purpose:
To provide funding to the Department of Housing to assist homeless
persons.
